# 📊 Superstore Sales Analytics Dashboard

## Project Overview

This project focuses on analyzing retail sales data to uncover meaningful business insights and support data-driven decision-making. Using Excel, I performed data cleaning, exploratory data analysis (EDA), and dashboard development to visualize key performance indicators and sales trends.

## Objectives

* Analyze overall sales and profit performance.
* Identify top-performing categories and products.
* Evaluate regional and segment-wise performance.
* Discover seasonal trends and business opportunities.
* Present insights through an interactive dashboard.

## Tools & Technologies

* Microsoft Excel
* Pivot Tables & Pivot Charts
* Data Cleaning
* Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
* Dashboard Design
* Business Analytics

## Key Business Insights

* Technology category generated the highest revenue.
* Office Supplies contributed the highest order volume.
* West and East regions showed the strongest sales performance.
* Sales peaked during Q4, indicating seasonal demand patterns.
* Certain products generated high sales but lower profit margins, highlighting optimization opportunities.

## Dashboard Features

* Sales Performance Analysis
* Profit Analysis
* Category & Sub-Category Performance
* Regional Analysis
* Customer Segment Analysis
* KPI Tracking
* Interactive Visualizations

## Skills Demonstrated

* Data Cleaning & Transformation
* Exploratory Data Analysis
* Data Visualization
* Dashboard Development
* KPI Analysis
* Business Insight Generation
* Data Storytelling

## Project Outcome

This project demonstrates how raw retail data can be transformed into actionable insights that help businesses improve performance, optimize strategies, and make informed decisions.

